Description: Handle of Knidian(?) pottery transport amphora. Rectangular stamp. Prow symbol.
Curator's comments: Only known from Petrie's drawing in his Journal, 1884-5, p.102,61. Not to be equated with British Museum 1925,0119.482, drawn by Petrie, p. 163, 5.
Bibliographic references: Villing et al 2013-2015 / Naukratis: Greeks in Egypt (JB.0225)
